label: Darwin Core type vocabulary terms
description: This term list was formerly used to indicate the type of Darwin Core resources.  It was deprecated in favor of class terms in the core terms namespace.

label: Darwin Core obsolete curatorial terms
description: This obsolete term list described curatorial terms.

label: Darwin Core obsolete core terms
description: This obsolete term list described core terms in the vocabulary.

label: Darwin Core obsolete geospatial terms
description: This obsolete term list described geospatial terms.

label: Obsolete Darwin Core terms that are not in a TDWG namespace
description: This list includes terms formerly cosidered to be a part of Darwin Core, but that are not part of a namespace controlled by TDWG  (http://rs.tdwg.org/).

label: Core terms defined by Darwin Core
description: This term list includes all currently valid terms that have been defined in the core Darwin Core namespace dwc:.  To comment on this schema, please create a new issue in https://github.com/tdwg/dwc/issues

label: TDWG utility terms
description: This list includes terms necessary to describe various TDWG vocabularies.

label: Darwin Core IRI-value Term Analogs
description: The terms on this list are intended to be used with IRI values

label: Core terms defined by Audubon Core
description: This term list includes all currently valid terms that have been defined in the core Audubon Core namespace ac:.

label: Darwin Core terms borrowed from the Dublin Core legacy namespace
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Darwin Core from the legacy (http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/) Dublin Core namespace

label: Darwin Core terms borrowed from the Dublin Core terms namespace
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Darwin Core from the terms (http://purl.org/dc/terms/) Dublin Core namespace

label: List of TDWG Executive decisions
description: Terms in this list are instances of the artificial tdwgutility:DecisionsClass class.

label: IPTC Photo Metadata Extension Iptc4xmpExt namespace terms borrowed by Audubon Core
description: This list includes Iptc4xmpExt namespace terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the IPTC Standard for Photo Metadata (http://www.iptc.org/std/photometadata/specification/IPTC-PhotoMetadata-201007_1.pdf).  Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: EXIF-specific terms from the XMP specification borrowed by Audubon core
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the XMP Specification Part 2, EXIF schema for EXIF-specific properties (https://wwwimages2.adobe.com/content/dam/acom/en/devnet/xmp/pdfs/XMP%20SDK%20Release%20cc-2016-08/XMPSpecificationPart2.pdf).  Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: IPTC Photo Metadata Extension photoshop namespace terms borrowed by Audubon Core
description: This list includes photoshop namespace terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the IPTC Standard for Photo Metadata (http://www.iptc.org/std/photometadata/specification/IPTC-PhotoMetadata-201007_1.pdf).  Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: XMP namespace terms from the XMP specification borrowed by Audubon Core
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the XMP Specification Part 1 - properties in the basic XMP namespace (https://wwwimages2.adobe.com/content/dam/acom/en/devnet/xmp/pdfs/XMP%20SDK%20Release%20cc-2016-08/XMPSpecificationPart1.pdf).  Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: XMP Rights Management namespace terms from the XMP specification borrowed by Audubon Core
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the XMP Specification Part 1 - properties in the XMP Rights Management namespace (https://wwwimages2.adobe.com/content/dam/acom/en/devnet/xmp/pdfs/XMP%20SDK%20Release%20cc-2016-08/XMPSpecificationPart1.pdf).  Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: Audubon Core terms borrowed from the Dublin Core legacy namespace
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the legacy (http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/) Dublin Core namespace

label: Audubon Core terms borrowed from the Dublin Core terms namespace
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from the terms (http://purl.org/dc/terms/) Dublin Core namespace

label: Audubon Core terms borrowed from Darwin Core
description: This list includes terms borrowed by Audubon Core from Darwin Core.
